---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 508
  - Title: Yesod Hayirah
    Location: 15
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Belief in the Unseen
  - 239
---
When thou standest before the Supreme King of kings to beg from Him
thy wants, remember who thou art, and what thy acts are, whether they
be straight or the reverse, and who the God is before whom thou
standest, who seeth into the darkest secret places.
